! Meta-Autotype Contingent Field

A deterministic fallback field emitted when an ingestion surface is unknown,
keeping the data inspectable without treating it as authoritative.

!! Why It Matters

It is the repo's answer to weird incoming artifacts: preserve the thing,
label uncertainty, and avoid silently flattening it into a false schema.

